review:
Before visiting to Dr.Anuprabha had been to other doctors for pregnancy with almost no results for years due to problem of PCOD. Dr Anuprabha is approachable for any queries at any time meanwhile , we started consulting her for three months which was very effective providing the solution to problems what is the issue and treatment .
Today happy to say the treatment was successful within few months , I suggest one of the best doctors in town . Always having a smile ,when you visit greetings makes you more comfortable .

review: Anu ma'am I have to say that she is a very knowledgeable doctor with lots of patience. I visited her on my relatives referral. I was worried of PCOD but her interaction and problem solving is really appreciated. She is very informative and warm in all her suggestions. She listened to all my doubts and gave good suggestions for both the issues of PCOD and my pregnancy which followed after 3 months of treatment for PCOD. Thank you very much ma'am. I refer her very much who need treatment for gynecological issues.
